<br>
This skill dumps their entire mana bar and creates a massive unresistable - yes UNRESISTABLE - nuke.<br>
<br>
The numbers coming out were from PvP (so add 30%) and are in the 17,000 DD range (= ~22,000 PvE).<br>
<br>
